BUILD FROM SOURCE
-----------------

Build production bundle:

$ bun run build

Clean and rebuild:

$ bun run rebuild

Type check only:

$ bun run typecheck

Run tests:

$ bun run test


PERFORMANCES
------------

Single file: ~2-5 seconds depending on network speed
Batch download: Up to 20 concurrent downloads with concurrency option
Memory usage: Optimized for long-running operations


